Installing\
		If you have downloaded an installer, it will do everything automatically for you.  Otherwise, please refer to the Manual installation paragraph below.\
\
The Jamoma distribution depend on certain 3rd party externals. For simplicity we have chosen to include these externals as part of the distribution. If you already have installed some or all of these externals, make sure that that the Jamoma distribution do not introduce older versions of the externals than you have already. All such externals can be found in the Jamoma/library/third-party folder.\
\
Requirements\
	\'95	Jamoma requires Cycling '74's Max version 5.0.7 or newer\
	\'95	Audio modules require Cycling '74's MSP (installed with Max).\
	\'95	Video modules require Cycling '74's Jitter (installed with Max).\
	\'95	Some Ambisonics spatialization modules require both Cycling '74's MSP and Jitter.\
\
