Getting started\
When you start Max5 the first time together with Jamoma, please go to Options->Object Defaults. Click on the lower left corner on the file symbol "load settings" and choose one of the color schemes starting with Jamoma, e.g. Jamoma Max.  \
The jamoma-overview.maxpat is certainly the best place to start, offering links to all Jamoma modules and components, as well as tutorials or examples.\
There are also some great online tutorials about using Jamoma and creating own Jamoma modules.\
If you are interested in creating your own modules, be sure to read the documentation (starting from /documentation/html), and the JIG (Jamoma Interface Guidelines) in particular. \
